{"tid":2491821,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"名古屋--高山--金澤六日五夜風景遊","createTime":"2021-04-16T14:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T06:44:22.000Z","uid":32,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c74af979edda4122f322cae1116cbc990fe73238","tid":2491821,"uid":32,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"繼2018年東京睇紅葉之後，2019年6月去咗名古屋--高山--金澤六日五夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機票用Asia Miles換，用咗35000里，回程係商務嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>東京風景Post</ins></strong><br />\n東京5日4夜睇風景<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2477042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2477042</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n------------------分隔線-------------------<br />\n食物相影得唔多，主要係睇風景，巴絲唔好屌得咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係行程嘅簡略版，淨係拎嚟參考㗎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n<br />\n綠洲21<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n<br />\n名古屋港水族館<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n<br />\n高山---上高地---新穗高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n<br />\n高山古街---白川鄉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\n<br />\n兼六園---金澤城---金澤21世紀美術館<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 6<br />\n<br />\n金澤站---機場<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"red\">開波</span></span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">Day 1</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為機會係換返嚟，所以要係台北轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmapNWcmynah3rkLikneKqF3unbjCRJjZcGdrhxnttp1vw?filename=vY64SVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvY64SVY.jpg&h=b3a93792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbXykkKPCgrFemjyQYmbJMN25TLaqSooRPPihoYwZsqXg?filename=CvXS1Uz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvXS1Uz.jpg&h=2b38321b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛咗粒機鐘到咗台北，手痕買咗幾盒鳳梨酥，好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdpBBZUjPtJbQxrxouEeC4DMdkzbJbJ7snGcTdD1KvBV2?filename=TA6P33z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTA6P33z.jpg&h=2140bec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠鐘上機喇，仲要落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPUHw5i2551nq53ybPnyUr6rEYArEMmM6S5GRAq1c6yia?filename=Uoy3o33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUoy3o33.jpg&h=ebec7f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY7JJeErcbTDVAByYyQpuw4ZpWZFgLUxpZNNcJcK9vJFd?filename=aa2PjCB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faa2PjCB.jpg&h=5dc7c208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗名古屋已經3點幾，搭埋車出去酒店已經4點幾<br />\n<br />\n呢次揀咗三井花園酒店名古屋普米爾酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNaH6ZZCGhxKXSiDsrjzBqrKSfKSKZoiEv5YEkbc5DVWw?filename=T27chpT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT27chpT.jpg&h=4644fde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme9zUoA7Fku2iCS2zk3FBpQDT6JLJ4ph5gF2Tr3rdihWS?filename=mmXr6im.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmXr6im.jpg&h=65bc46a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後落去浸咗陣酒店個溫泉，然後落咗大須觀音商店街行咗陣<br />\n<br />\n衝咗入間燒肉食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmanW3SctqLdwRGEPS189VW8zMkHKmaPA11judkV4hyiYB?filename=Dqd3o7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqd3o7G.jpg&h=b9f12a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXWBTYtakMukwjsjKevybqhsR3MznnN1bTNB77F1dq84e?filename=O7AJo7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7AJo7M.jpg&h=7f9c8386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後去咗綠洲21影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n途經貢茶勁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ8CD9YcJCkJBLAvNpJfZX4Y47CijZFWLhsMnqY2nSs2v?filename=Kf3rmUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKf3rmUZ.jpg&h=e8ea1676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf4pVcKizxbTWo1HeA4knsPfEcChEf9DW5BfPkYaHZZbu?filename=34z938G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34z938G.jpg&h=ede6de07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma76Jxk7zEngc4wJi3fEE1J4oc57WDAmkuA2dsp5S3wYJ?filename=WiVmaOJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiVmaOJ.jpg&h=514b5c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTcsQaekE1uBJEyVx3mZYg7Ru1B4TrYRNNZ4YrpaEyNab?filename=3veYXtK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3veYXtK.jpg&h=58610489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXrVhyWP4MPs94BRsgA53PNuQ9c8WL9GUKmPXQLH1iXst?filename=95GP38M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95GP38M.jpg&h=d2985e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行完之後太攰，返咗酒店休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPrx2HznQ4hqykPsnCetBFNY77cDNCTKcvXRqCGCiuG4R?filename=z9LEGVP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9LEGVP.jpg&h=5774a2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n待續........."},{"pid":"483c77726e5ce2108b9d5f3358c94d2727019d26","tid":2491821,"uid":29979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳下<br />\n<br />\n希望在英港人會盡自己公民權力<br />\n<br />\n2021 倫敦市長選舉直擊 Farah London 定 Shaun Bailey!?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2491802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2491802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47f584e4b39ac5197dbf5d1f4bb4cba29796ccf7","tid":2491821,"uid":32,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n一早執好哂行李，去咗名古屋水族館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNhqgyVBLKUGzTMRFoSPJE5EjSXKnkEHrKR1heK8Qkusa?filename=mWhDc3T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWhDc3T.jpg&h=aeafb440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYNJepX5A8ioYZ4vzk4VRPPiXhcMR1qoatoJvr6QM4Wyp?filename=Ws3bx38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWs3bx38.jpg&h=df437f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmden2JneWiJB1JDs5MeUr9ek49VfucMjtnTciLkZgcPWL?filename=TJG4S4i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJG4S4i.jpg&h=ded97637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPrhcQJupzwN7KDorbqjHWk7jkMX92xgqP7Gy93aKh9iW?filename=wvCvOCO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwvCvOCO.jpg&h=e974401a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZe3t94X9EojfQDEFRqRkFJRDYMbCUa41iJ1Q4o1KcjHF?filename=z3YrmXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3YrmXX.jpg&h=bb995395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd2Y1uroFK24Yc4jxSTDn4RtdSnKJmbwske2m3b5TdNkV?filename=vh5EGX9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvh5EGX9.jpg&h=17180640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到入去，見到就快到表演時間，於是坐低睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPh79y6scSo9rotkmpVXPKqLK2wMGqAFfNJ3Mea5LDqnF?filename=iJwgKbQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJwgKbQ.jpg&h=54997ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd8iZatpuAe3CV2rfB3ccNNMCpzy7psU9vCoFvHgVxwar?filename=83jx1Yx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83jx1Yx.jpg&h=d773cc6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https: